cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR

This paper is primarily focused on instance segmentation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The pipeline introduced in the paper involves 3D scanning and reasoning, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of GAN-based domain adaptation techniques also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper involves the creation of a new dataset, which could be relevant to graphics (cs.GR).
